label: A17B3_cF160_227_aeg_bc-001
title: Na$_{24-\delta}$Ge$_{136}$ Clathrate Structure
comments:
This is a metastable type II clathrate structure.  Only 2/3 of the Na (8b) sites are occupied, making the actual composition Na$_{21.33}$Ge$_{136}$ (Na$_{1.253}$Ge$_{17}$). 
 We use the Rietveld refinement data from (Feng, 2021).
